# Collapsible Sidebar – Elevvo Pathways

This project is part of the Elevvo Pathways internship tasks.  
It demonstrates a **responsive collapsible sidebar** built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**, featuring smooth toggle animations and a clean layout.

---

## ✨ Features
- Sidebar with logo placeholder and navigation links  
- Toggle button to open/close sidebar  
- Smooth CSS/JS animations  
- Mobile-friendly responsive design  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **HTML5** – structure  
- **CSS3** – styling & animations  
- **JavaScript (ES6)** – toggle logic  


---

